MAIN.original: ~s~Use ~INPUT_PHONE_TAKE_OUT~ and ~INPUT_PHONE_PUT_AWAY~ to navigate the phone menu.
~s~Use ~INPUT_KB_UP~ and ~INPUT_KB_DOWN~ to navigate the phone menu.
Press ~INPUT_PHONE_ACCEPT~ to select a menu item.
Press ~INPUT_PHONE_CANCEL~ to exit the phone menu and put away the phone.
MAIN.translated: 按~INPUT_PHONE_CANCEL~退出手机菜单或收起手机。

MAIN.original: ~s~The special icon above the radar is a mission replay text message. Press ~INPUT_PHONE_TAKE_OUT~ to read this message and select the ~h~replay~s~ option to replay the last mission you failed.
MAIN.translated: ~s~小地图上方的特殊图标是重玩任务的短信。按~INPUT_PHONE_TAKE_OUT~阅读短信后选择~h~重玩~s~可以重新开始刚才失败的任务。

MAIN.original: Hold ~INPUT_AIM~ to lock onto enemies. Press ~INPUT_ATTACK~ to fire your weapon.
MAIN.translated: 按住~INPUT_AIM~锁定敌人。按下~INPUT_ATTACK~开火。

MAIN.original: When locked onto enemies you can switch between targets using ~PAD_RSTICK_LEFTRIGHT~.
MAIN.translated: 锁定敌人时，你可以通过~PAD_RSTICK_LEFTRIGHT~切换目标。

MAIN.original: Half hold ~PAD_LT~ to free aim. Use ~PAD_RSTICK_ALL~ to aim (Standard controls).
MAIN.translated: 半按~PAD_LT~可以自由瞄准。使用~PAD_RSTICK_ALL~瞄准。(标准键位下)

MAIN.translated: ~s~若想快速加入一局多人游戏，请选择手机菜单中的即刻加入。

MAIN.original: Hold ~INPUT_SPRINT~ to run. Tap ~INPUT_SPRINT~ repeatedly to sprint.
Press ~INPUT_DUCK~ to crouch, this will make your aim more accurate.
MAIN.translated: 按~INPUT_DUCK~蹲下，蹲下时瞄准精度更高。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Man... I dunno right now. Shit, I'll call you back.

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~I dunno. Ain't it enough that I'm calling for help? Fucking bureaucrats.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~不知道。光打过来求救还不管用吗？傻逼官僚主义。

MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~您好，这里是LCPD，请问您想让我们向哪里出警？

MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~您好，您呼叫的是医疗服务中心，您需要在哪里的医疗应急？

MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~您好，这里是FDLC，您需要在哪里的帮助？

MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~您好，您呼叫的是自由城应急服务。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Please use your touchtone keypad to select which specific service you require.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~请使用您的拨号按键选择您需要的特定服务。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Press 1 for Police, press 2 for Paramedics, press 3 for the Fire Department.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~报警请按1，急救请按2，消防请按3。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~An LCPD peacekeeper will be there as soon as possible, sir.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~很快将有一名LCPD干员到达，先生。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~We'll send a basically trained paramedic as soon as we can, sir.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我们会尽快派出一支训练有素的医疗小组，先生。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Don't move and please have your insurance documentation or credit card ready.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~请不要离开，并准备好您的保险单证或信用卡。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~We'll get a fire truck out to you right away.
~z~~x~Hold tight and please be advised that the FDLC takes no responsibility for damage to property.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~请坚持住。注意，FDLC不对过程中造成的财产损失负任何责任。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~We look forward to hearing from you again. Please stay safe in the meantime.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我们期待您的下次来电。同时请您注意安全。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~I'm sorry, but all our peacekeepers are currently busy filling quotas and dealing with paper work.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~很抱歉，但目前我们的干员都忙于完成指标以及书面工作。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~All our lines are busy at the moment, please call again later. Your emergency is important to us.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~目前我们的电话全部占线，请稍后再拨。您的紧急状况对我们十分重要。

MAIN.original: ~z~What's the point in the Second Amendment if you ain't gonna use it?

MAIN.original: ~z~It don't matter what the world thinks of America, at least we can still buy guns here.
MAIN.translated: ~z~世界上其他人怎么评价美国不重要，至少我们还能买到枪。

MAIN.translated: ~z~别担心，哥们。经济再萧条也影响不到黑市军火。

MAIN.translated: ~z~你们缺代言人吗？失落帮正在找赞助商。

MAIN.original: ~z~Thanks man. The next guy I shoot, I'm going to tell him where I shop.
MAIN.translated: ~z~谢了，兄弟。下次开枪前，我会告诉目标你的店的。

MAIN.original: ~z~Didn't take me for a window shopper, did you? So long.
~z~Sorry, man. I had to cut down spending on firearms. This fucking economic downturn...
MAIN.translated: ~z~抱歉，兄弟。武器这块只能消费降级了。都他妈怪经济衰退...

MAIN.original: ~z~You know what, I thought I was gonna go out and kill somebody then I decided not to.
MAIN.translated: ~z~知道吗，本来我想出门杀几个人，想想还是算了。

MAIN.original: ~z~I was just looking, man. Guns give me a raging hard on.
MAIN.translated: ~z~我就看看，兄弟。枪会让我兽性大发的。

MAIN.original: ~z~Fuck it, man. My wife don't need killing after all.
MAIN.translated: ~z~他妈的，兄弟。我老婆不需要我杀人来着。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~What kinda engine you got in this thing?
~z~~x~Just let me look at the city in peace, man.
~z~~x~You like bikes? I gotta nice one.
~z~~x~You're a nasty little madam, ain't ya?
~z~~x~You're young and beautiful. Don't throw it away, baby.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~你年轻靓丽，别浪费了啊，宝贝。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Shit, have I seen that booty on the internet?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~妈的，这屁股我好像在网上见过？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Sweet girls like the bad boys, don't they?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~小可爱都喜欢坏男孩，不是吗？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You ever done it one the back of a chopper going a hundred down the super slab?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~你有在飞驰的摩托车后面这样过吗？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You like ink, baby? Scope me out.
~z~~x~You got a big brother I should worry about.
~z~~x~You like weed and beer? We could have a good old night.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~喜欢大麻跟啤酒吗？我们可以好好来一晚。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Excuse those stains sugar. It's only grease, that's all it is.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~恕我衣服有点脏。油渍罢了，没什么的。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~I can only fit one of you ladies on my bike with me.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我的摩托只能带一位女士回去。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Hey, hey, hey, you're ganging up on me. I might have to fight back.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~喂喂喂，你们想多对一吗？这我就要反击了。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~I'm seeing double and I ain't even drunk.
~z~~x~Stick a fork in me, I'm done.
~z~~x~Memories of that shit are gonna keep me going if I ever do time.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~这次的场景会让我久久不能忘怀的。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You just got yourself a part in my dreams, baby.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~你已经在我的梦中拥有一席之地了，宝贝。
